Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.79,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}如伊卡洛斯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:16.42,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}那份纯真的勇气如今已不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:18.77,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我们活着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.87,0:00:22.14,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}将那平凡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.18,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}平凡无奇地度过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:28.84,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}怀着无数问号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:36.66,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}寻找答案 却陷入迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:44.06,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}若能得知 答案的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:50.63,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}一切将化作崭新的音色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.69,0:00:53.18,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这阵风的尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:58.87,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}定会有真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.78,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.39,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}这些泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.98,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}总有一天会干涸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.99,0:01:13.08,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很困难
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.22,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}即使现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:22.27,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}只需微微一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:24.98,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1}便能迎着清风 乱了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:28.97,OPCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\be1}勇往直前吧
