Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.75,0:22:32.00,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}当两人漂移不定的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.95,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}相互触碰之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.09,0:22:40.88,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻 你在想着谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:46.61,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}隔着玻璃晃过的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.65,0:22:48.51,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那忧伤的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.64,0:22:54.85,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}距离那么近 却无法触及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:59.32,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}积累种种借口
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.17,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}逃避着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:10.19,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}那时几近崩溃的软弱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:13.54,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}此刻仿佛已能面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.67,0:23:15.22,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Love in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.26,0:23:17.65,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}打开门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.77,0:23:21.13,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}前往有你的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:28.20,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}告诉你这份焦灼已久的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:29.88,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}Feel my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.96,0:23:35.80,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}在你坦然露出笑容的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:39.35,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:43.15,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}会让我的泪水更坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:48.55,EDCN1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur3}You are my only shooting star
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.11,0:01:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆杀了少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了向耀眼的银河世界进发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将少女鲜红的血注入了船的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果 萨姆爱上的不是少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是对银河世界的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱的少女从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不过是装点旅行道路的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船载着萨姆 驶向了银河世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而萨姆很快发觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾经那样憧憬银河世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 那里的星辰和生他养他的鱼之星球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有多大的不同？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼之星球也是银河里的一颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河并非遥远的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨姆从一开始就是那璀璨世界的住人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 萨姆又是为了什么杀了少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.91,0:02:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事真的就此结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.95,0:02:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的故事我听够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很拘谨哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不拘谨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拘谨啦 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.52,0:03:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天晚上 谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在教室里说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我就是很想道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必客气 我只是随性而行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.44,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君 明知自己说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是驯化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.29,0:04:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是觉得不舒服 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 很拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉须方君好冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天他们俩一起请假也不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是发生了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.35,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三个都是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为前天拓人君和扬卷同学约会了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉你们三个之间都好拘谨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个…我也有份吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.81,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打了我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想找死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拘谨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绮罗星十字团总会现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 驯化了Samekh的进藤须方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从沉眠中觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Samekh（柱）的驭星者终于诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而Samekh本体的全貌还未得以确认
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使他拥有强力的第1阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不敌能够驱动素体本身的第2阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.67,0:05:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,计划无需改变
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒Tauburn就能当首领的规则也不变吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.82,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则不变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有必要重新考虑我方的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好认为进藤须方和那个津名志拓人是同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有可能在素体的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.15,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用进藤须方强力的第1阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.17,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在第2阶段的战斗中利用第1阶段的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎心情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了是谁去收买Samekh的驭星者却失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 考虑到Samekh的驭星者已觉醒的现状
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最优先的课题是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移至第3阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则 就赢不了Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得你这么没底气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又从你手中溜走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们本来就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所珍视的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是因一时的感情而放过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.59,0:07:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那礼物 要退货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不能像以前那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一阵子再以别的理由送他？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸不太合 我想去换
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要上车我要上车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这一招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小狐狸 小狐狸 小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去渡船停泊场是坐这辆车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面第3个站下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我今早还被关在一个大鸟笼中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.37,0:09:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我喜欢将我关起来的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.15,0:09:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以其实也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也说喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有这种彼此喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却无法顺利发展的关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我还是要离开岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.14,0:09:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人重新来过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.61,0:09:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位也请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相位显示器 数据中转
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择E方式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ADPS启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输入远程任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加速模拟 在5号至8号区进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作真卖力啊 格林教授
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光彩照人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光彩照人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉游刃有余呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游刃有余？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的猩红之吻也感觉莫名地游刃有余
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我重塑 排除成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么开始追踪 之后交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设定标记光束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.46,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的第1阶段是可以操纵吻过的男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.40,0:10:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她亲了谁 不难猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就见识见识她的本事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经是属于我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.47,0:11:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么严肃的表情 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和须方谈谈 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.65,0:11:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是男人之间的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:53.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jaguar？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕…和子大人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.53,0:12:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我支开了虎豹姐妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那二人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了防我走出岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身边随时准备杀我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有柱之印的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.03,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放出岛外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进藤家族 自古以来有这样的家规
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 从小孩子的时候开始就一直被监视
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子的时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就随身带刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子 说她一直在意这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:59.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说她害怕但不敢问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从没真心对过别人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是建起屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独自待在遥远的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 今天很激动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被关在岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟和子那种绝望的感觉你能明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭你这个外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子她 根本没有放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子她这么说了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 绮罗星的所有素体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会全部摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和子她 终有一天能离开这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.82,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 和子手里的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是给你的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是明知却没有收下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.82,0:14:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诫过你别轻易对我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.11,0:14:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会喜欢或者讨厌一个人到想杀他的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有关心过我到起杀意的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 连自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.85,0:14:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实也就是放任自流而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己 和我不也是同一类人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 从遇见你那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直对你抱有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明知可能死还游来 是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想骗过我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一探究竟是吗 对自己的生死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说我没有真心对人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢 有多真心？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动真格的话不会就那种程度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非那种程度的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫嚣着要保护和子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 根本无须动用王之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:17.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀你根本不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 尽管挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.66,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你知道自己有几两重
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零时空间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进藤须方已经
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为我猩红之吻一阶的俘虏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的一切都已经是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方那庞大的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,填满了我的Peshent（口）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经由Samekh强化的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这台Peshent是无敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且津名志拓人与进藤须方是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种情况下他无法作战
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击败银河美少年的是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,须方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了 须方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.94,0:19:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？果然了得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猩红之吻的一阶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能如此完美的控制对象物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他在开动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Peshent被支配了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这种程度吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要让和子伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.01,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看错你了 须方！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.32,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把小刀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为保护和子带在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真够笨拙的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上长大的乡下人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 外乡人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都在…笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Peshent承受不了Samekh的能量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生的冒险仍在继续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.11,0:23:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新加入剧团夜间飞行的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野酱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而绮罗星十字团的新干部登场
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.18,0:24:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水野其人的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.10,0:24:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家再见了
